@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.18)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.08)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.58) / v2))
    v1 = (0.90 / 0.70)
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
